snippet.title: Skrillex Quest: 100% Playthrough
snippet.description:
How to collect 7/7 scrolls, every treasure and the Master Sword.

Also note that, to kill 58 enemies, you have to kill at least five glitches at the first area. I found it to be the hardest part, since you don't have much time and sometimes the enemies get kicked very far from you when you hit them, so you might rely a bit on luck there.
